_Hif’il_ Imperative: The _hif’il_ binyan has an [[{{imperative}} form]], which is one of the [[Hif’il Forms|forms of the _hif’il_ binyan]].
- The _Hif’il_ imperative form has [[_Hif’il_ Imperative for regular shorushim|conjugations for regular shorushim]].
- The _Hif’il_ imperative form has conjugations for irregular shorushim which will be added at a later time.
